These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, security-guard, lawyer, photographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, action, animation, zombie
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, cat, fish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, soccer, cycling, skateboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, boat, taxi
 1. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching zombie movies is the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 9. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
10. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
11. the coach is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
12. the owner of the cat is between the person watching animation movies and the owner of the horse##2
13. the lawyer is the person driving the taxi##1
14. the person driving the boat is the security-guard##1
15. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the security-guard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Job           | coach | lawyer | photographer  | security-guard    |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | zombie   | animation  | scientific  |
| Pet           | horse        | cat    | fish        | bird |
| Sport         | skateboarding    | soccer      | rugby   | cycling    |
| Transport     | bus  | taxi     | jet-ski | boat |

