.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, drawing, sudoku, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, adventure, spy, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, techno, house, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, sailing, skiing, rugby
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
 4. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
10. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who's sport is rugby##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
12. the fan of indie is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the fan of techno is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea        | soy-milk       | hot-chocolate    | coffee       |
| Hobby         | sudoku | drawing      | dancing | writing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | spy | adventure  | fantasy   |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | rock         | indie   | house      |
| Sport         | sailing      | baseball     | skiing    | rugby      |

