.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, banana, cauliflower, grapefruit
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, entrepreneur, project-manager, chef
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, trance, funk, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, skiing, water-polo, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, tram, boat, bus
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is the fan of trance##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 3. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
 5. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 7. the chef is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 8. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating cauliflower is the fan of funk##1
11. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
12. the fan of pop is on the right of the project-manager##1
13. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person eating grapefruit##1
14. the fan of funk is on the left of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | cauliflower | banana | zucchini     | grapefruit |
| Job           | project-manager  | chef   | freelancer | entrepreneur  |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | pop      | trance     | d&b   |
| Sport         | handball | skateboarding  | skiing   | water-polo    |
| Transport     | boat | tram    | bus     | trike |

