.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, puzzles, reading, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, videographer, engineer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, pop, punk, gospel
4 different pets are kept: rat, ferret, dog, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, trike, roller, airplane
 1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the fan of punk is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 4. the fan of gospel is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the roller##2
 5. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 8. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the trike##1
 9. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
10. the electrician is on the left of the doctor##1
11. the engineer is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is camping is the engineer##1
13. the engineer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
14. the electrician is on the left or right of the doctor##3
15. the videographer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | sudoku | puzzles    | camping | reading       |
| Job           | electrician | doctor  | engineer   | videographer |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | pop     | gospel      | punk            |
| Pet           | rat       | dog      | ferret    | rabbit           |
| Transport     | airplane      | roller | trike   | scooter         |

