4 different pets are kept: fish, pony, rabbit, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, swimming, rugby, cricket
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person eating kiwi##2
 2. the analyst is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the analyst##1
 4. the musician is in an even position##4
 5. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 9. the pilot is the person eating carrot##1
10. the person eating kiwi is the person watching crime movies##1
11. the pilot is the person watching zombie movies##1
12. the owner of the rabbit is the person watching satire movies##1
13. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
14. the person eating kiwi is the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |       4        |
