 6. the doctor is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the entrepreneur is the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating corn is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
13. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4
14. the entrepreneur is between the person eating corn and the person who's hobby is singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
