10. the person eating cherry is in an even position##4
11. the turkish is on the right of the polish##1
12. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the dancer##3
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
14. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the italian##1
