.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, juice, cola
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, lemon, papaya, lime
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, skydiving, reading, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, family, spy, epic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, snowboarding, ice-hockey, tennis
 1. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's hobby is reading##2
 7. the person drinking cola is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching epic movies##2
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person eating lemon is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice    | cola      | milk      | iced-tea |
| Food          | kiwi | papaya | lime       | lemon |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | filmmaking   | skydiving | reading  |
| Movie-Genre   | spy    | family    | epic      | musical   |
| Sport         | swimming   | snowboarding     | ice-hockey       | tennis  |

