.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, sudoku, camping, board-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer, doctor, coach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, country, hip-hop, gospel
4 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, bird, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller, boat, bus
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is the owner of the rat##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the coach is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 6. the doctor is on the left of the lawyer##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is the coach##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is the owner of the rat##1
 9. the person driving the boat is between the fan of hip-hop and the lawyer##2
10. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the fan of country##1
13. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
14. the lawyer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | baking       | sudoku    | board-games | camping     |
| Job           | coach | doctor  | lawyer  | entrepreneur       |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop         | r&b        | gospel     | country |
| Pet           | turtle    | bird   | rat       | snake     |
| Transport     | bus          | boat | quad-bike      | roller |

