.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: papaya, watermelon, pineapple, pear
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, security-guard, manager, nurse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, western, family, musical
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, train, scooter
 1. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
 2. the nurse is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the architect is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is between the person drinking tea and the security-guard##2
 6. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
 8. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
 9. the security-guard is the person eating pear##1
10. the person watching western movies is the person eating pineapple##1
11. the nurse is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
12. the person watching scientific movies is between the person driving the train and the person watching western movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |     3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee          | tea     | almond-milk       | sprite |
| Food          | watermelon    | papaya      | pineapple   | pear          |
| Job           | manager   | nurse | architect   | security-guard   |
| Movie-Genre   | family | scientific    | western     | musical        |
| Transport     | train         | helicopter    | scooter | bike           |

