There 4 different types of food: cabbage, banana, peach, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, woodworking, magic-tricks
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, musical, drama, martial-arts
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, roller, quad-bike, ship
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 3. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person eating peach is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
11. the person driving the taxi is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the person eating mango is the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
